  "detailed_description": "<h1>Subscribe to our Newsletter</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751710/extras/fb438ad093df36a22a51dac751b1541d.avif?t=1758528193\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>You are trapped alone in a room, with only a screen giving you orders and a locked door for company. But still, you’re feeling watched…Is there a chance at escape if you just do what you’re told?<br><br>The only way to freedom is through that locked door but there seems to be something…. or someone on the other side telling you not to obey.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751710/extras/dfd7a21a4c1d31521e977a3e22b83a22.webp?t=1758528193\" width=32 height=32 /></span> A dark exploration of Maslow’s Hierarchy of Needs<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751710/extras/49570e7f04280a646fff1acf20b965ea.webp?t=1758528193\" width=32 height=32 /></span> An escape room you’re not sure you should escape<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751710/extras/a5dc82b092086c8b2e34cfc1cd953213.webp?t=1758528193\" width=32 height=32 /></span> And the question of how far you would go if you thought there was a way out<br><br>Dive into our short chilling interactive horror experience of 15 to 20 mins to find out if you will comply!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751710/extras/edb4ccb45646c17f1e981f0ae6aecaad.avif?t=1758528193\" width=616 height=140 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751710/extras/fb438ad093df36a22a51dac751b1541d.avif?t=1758528193\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>You are trapped alone in a room, with only a screen giving you orders and a locked door for company. But still, you’re feeling watched…Is there a chance at escape if you just do what you’re told?<br><br>The only way to freedom is through that locked door but there seems to be something…. or someone on the other side telling you not to obey.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751710/extras/dfd7a21a4c1d31521e977a3e22b83a22.webp?t=1758528193\" width=32 height=32 /></span> A dark exploration of Maslow’s Hierarchy of Needs<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751710/extras/49570e7f04280a646fff1acf20b965ea.webp?t=1758528193\" width=32 height=32 /></span> An escape room you’re not sure you should escape<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751710/extras/a5dc82b092086c8b2e34cfc1cd953213.webp?t=1758528193\" width=32 height=32 /></span> And the question of how far you would go if you thought there was a way out<br><br>Dive into our short chilling interactive horror experience of 15 to 20 mins to find out if you will comply!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1751710/extras/edb4ccb45646c17f1e981f0ae6aecaad.avif?t=1758528193\" width=616 height=140 /></span>",
